</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="22.[163,1070,830,910]" pageId="22" pageNumber="1167">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[562,669,830,851]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="1167">championi</emphasis>
, is a patronym dedicated to George Charles Champion for his dedicated efforts in enhancing our knowledge of Middle American beetles.
</paragraph>
